title: The Night Lynsie Disappeared
description: The mystery of a college student who disappeared after a night out clubbing stumps investigators for years. Her mother thought she was at a sleepover with friends and it took an eagle-eyed detective to find the truth buried in a pile of lies. Josh Mankiewicz reports.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
